metadata.name: BOYZ II BEASTS - ALPHABEASTS GUMBO TRAILER 1
metadata.description:
BOYZ II BEASTS - ALPHABEASTS GUMBO TRAILER 1 is a 1/1 NFT a part of the “Alphabeasts Gumbo” collection. “Alphabeasts Gumbo” is the inaugural collection under Mike Reesé’s BOYZ II BEASTS project. The 26 Tribes of Alphabeasts are hieroglyphic animations of the alphabet that correspond to 26 unique emotions, moods or expressions relative to the life experience. Each Alphabeast is hand drawn then digitally rendered and there are 6 iterations of an Alphabeast in a single NFT. This collection will be limited to 26 1/1 NFT artworks.

BOYZ II BEASTS - ALPHABEASTS GUMBO TRAILER 1  contains a sonic landscape curated by The Burning Benjamins and was edited by Dennis Hope.

Each holder of this collection will be whitelisted for the upcoming completely generative "Alphabeasts Gumbo" Generation 2 collection in 2022.
